\paragraph{\textbf{Phase stability}}
To understand the phase stability of CuSbTe$_2$, I have attempted to simulate its phase diagram using Thermo-Calc software. However, the results were unsatisfactory despite the availability of the Semiconducting material database (version 5.3), Thermo-Calc (2025a) failed to generate any stable pure phase for this system. This leaves the problem open-ended, necessitating a first-principles approach. We are currently exploring this direction.
